  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/bb83c70c4edaa7f8ca53f6cd84b172d5.poster.avif?t=1761751854\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/bb83c70c4edaa7f8ca53f6cd84b172d5.webm?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/bb83c70c4edaa7f8ca53f6cd84b172d5.mp4?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Scrap is an independent third-person shooter that takes place in a futuristic world inhabited by robots.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/5142ff35fce4c7beae68ed29b8741f5c.poster.avif?t=1761751854\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/5142ff35fce4c7beae68ed29b8741f5c.webm?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/5142ff35fce4c7beae68ed29b8741f5c.mp4?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Meet B9-X, a robot from the scrapyard who turns out to be the only hope in the fight against aggressive aliens.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/e4e3ac40b5261c855401f031a4b45f94.poster.avif?t=1761751854\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/e4e3ac40b5261c855401f031a4b45f94.webm?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/e4e3ac40b5261c855401f031a4b45f94.mp4?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Constant struggle</h2>Defeat dozens of dangerous opponents.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/f7473f9d7ae29aed68b72e351e6ad3e5.poster.avif?t=1761751854\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/f7473f9d7ae29aed68b72e351e6ad3e5.webm?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/f7473f9d7ae29aed68b72e351e6ad3e5.mp4?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic gameplay</h2>Jump into the action, use futuristic weapons, move agilely, and deliver melee attacks.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/c3588b92c468b08c5da54152df47886c.poster.avif?t=1761751854\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/c3588b92c468b08c5da54152df47886c.webm?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/c3588b92c468b08c5da54152df47886c.mp4?t=1761751854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Various covers</h2>Use covers to avoid getting hit.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304650/extras/251111c9974f63f5990d3ae71c6bd5ac.poster.avif?t=1761751854\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/